#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The wallet subsystem provides a convenient and secure way to manage all your "
"passwords."
msgstr ""
"Podsistem denarnice ponuja priročen in varen način za upravljanje vseh vaših "
"gesel."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kwallet"
msgstr "Kwallet"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "passwords"
msgstr "gesla"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "forms"
msgstr "obrazci"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Computer users have a very large amount of data to manage, some of which is "
"sensitive. In particular, you will typically have many passwords to manage. "
"Remembering them is difficult and writing them down on paper or in a text "
"file is insecure."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniki računalnikov imajo za upravljanje zelo veliko količino podatkov, "
"od katerih so nekateri občutljivi. Zlasti običajno boste imeli veliko gesel "
"za upravljanje. Zapomniti si jih je težko, zapis na papir ali besedilno "
"datoteko pa nevaren."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; provides a secure way to store passwords and other secret "
"information, allowing the user to remember only a single password instead of "
"numerous different passwords and credentials."
msgstr ""
"&kwallet5; zagotavlja varen način za shranjevanje gesel in drugih tajnih "
"podatkov, kar uporabniku omogoča, da si zapomni samo eno geslo namesto "
"številnih različnih gesel in poverilnic."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a Wallet"
msgstr "Ustvarite denarnico"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Wallet is a password storage. It is usually sufficient to have just one "
"wallet secured by one master password but you can organize your large "
"collection of passwords by wallets using &kwalletmanager5;."
msgstr ""
"Denarnica je shramba gesel. Običajno zadostuje, da imate samo eno denarnico, "
"zaščiteno z enim glavnim geslom, vendar lahko svojo veliko zbirko gesel "
"organizirate po denarnicah z &kwalletmanager5;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default a wallet named <guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel> will be used to "
"store your passwords. This wallet is secured by your login password and will "
"automatically be opened at login, if kwallet_pam is installed and properly "
"configured. On certain distros (&eg; Archlinux) kwallet_pam is not installed "
"by default"
msgstr ""
"Privzeto bo za shranjevanje vaših gesel uporabljena denarnica z imenom "
"<guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel>. Ta denarnica je zaščitena z vašim geslom za "
"prijavo in se samodejno odpre ob prijavi, če je kwallet_pam nameščen in "
"pravilno konfiguriran. V nekaterih distribucijah (&eg; Archlinux) "
"kwallet_pam ni privzeto nameščen"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other wallets have to be opened manually."
msgstr "Druge denarnice je treba odpreti ročno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two ways to create a new wallet:"
msgstr "Novo denarnico lahko ustvarite na dva načina:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the menu item <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New "
"Wallet</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the &kwalletmanager5;"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite menijski element <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Nova denarnica</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v aplikaciji "
"&kwalletmanager5;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>New</guibutton> button in the &systemsettings; module "
"<guilabel>KDE Wallet</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <guibutton>Novo</guibutton> v &systemsettings; modul "
"<guilabel>Denarnica KDE</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have not created a wallet yet, see section <link linkend=\"kwallet-"
"using\">Using &kwallet5;</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če še niste ustvarili denarnice, glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"kwallet-"
"using\">Uporaba &kwallet5;</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kwallet5; offers two different ways to store your data:"
msgstr "&kwallet5; ponuja dva različna načina za shranjevanje vaših podatkov:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Select encryption</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izberite šifriranje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Select encryption</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izberite šifriranje</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Blowfish encryption"
msgstr "Šifriranje Blowfish"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; saves this sensitive data for you in a strongly encrypted file, "
"accessible by all applications, and protected with a master password that "
"you define."
msgstr ""
"&kwallet5; shrani te občutljive podatke za vas v močno šifrirano datoteko, "
"ki je dostopna vsem aplikacijam in je zaščitena z glavnim geslom, ki ga "
"določite sami."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Create a blowfish encrypted wallet</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Ustvarite šifrirano denarnico blowfish</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Create a blowfish encrypted wallet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Ustvarite šifrirano denarnico blowfish</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The data is encrypted with the <ulink url=\"http://www.schneier.com/blowfish."
"html\">Blowfish symmetric block cipher algorithm</ulink>, the algorithm key "
"is derived from the <ulink url=\"http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3174.txt\">SHA-1 "
"hash</ulink> of the password, with a key length of 156 bits (20 bytes). The "
"data into the wallet file is also hashed with SHA-1 and checked before the "
"data is deciphered and accessible by the applications."
msgstr ""
"Podatki so šifrirani z <ulink url=\"http://www.schneier.com/blowfish.html"
"\">algoritmom simetrične blokovne šifre Blowfish</ulink>, ključ algoritma "
"izhaja iz <ulink url=\"http: //www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3174.txt\">SHA-1 hash</"
"ulink> gesla z dolžino ključa 156 bitov (20 bajtov). Podatki v datoteki "
"denarnice so tudi zgoščeni s SHA-1 in preverjeni, preden so podatki "
"dešifrirani in dostopni aplikacijam."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "GPG encryption"
msgstr "GPG šifriranje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"GnuPG offers some very strong encryption algorithms and uses passphrase "
"protected long keys."
msgstr ""
"GnuPG ponuja nekaj zelo močnih algoritmov šifriranja in uporablja dolge "
"ključe, zaščitene z geslom."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>No GPG key found</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Ključ GPG ni bil najden</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>No GPG key found</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Ključ GPG ni bil najden</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The screenshots above show the case where an encryption capable GPG key was "
"not found on the system. Please use applications like &kgpg; or &kleopatra; "
"to create a key and try again."
msgstr ""
"Zgornji posnetki zaslona prikazujejo primer, ko ključ GPG, ki je zmožen "
"šifriranja, ni bil najden v sistemu. Uporabite programe, kot je &kgpg; ali "
"&kleopatra; ustvarite ključ in poskusite znova."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a GPG key was found you will get the next dialog where you can select a "
"key to use for your new wallet."
msgstr ""
"Če je bil najden ključ GPG, se prikaže naslednje pogovorno okno, v katerem "
"lahko izberete ključ za svojo novo denarnico."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Select an encryption key</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izberite šifrirni ključ</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Select an encryption key</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izberite šifrirni ključ</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; will now use GPG when storing wallets and when opening them. The "
"passphrase dialog only shows once. Even if the wallet is closed after "
"initial open, subsequent opening will occur silently during the same session."
msgstr ""
"&kwallet5; bo zdaj uporabljal GPG pri shranjevanju denarnic in pri njihovem "
"odpiranju. Pogovorno okno gesla se prikaže samo enkrat. Tudi če je denarnica "
"zaprta po začetnem odprtju, bo naslednje odpiranje potekalo tiho med isto "
"sejo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same session can handle simultaneously both file formats. &kwallet5; "
"will transparently detect the file format and load the correct backend to "
"handle it."
msgstr ""
"Ista seja lahko obravnava obe obliki datotek hkrati. &kwallet5; bo pregledno "
"zaznal obliko datoteke in naložil pravilno zaledje za njeno obravnavo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use your sensitive data from your classic wallet with the new backend "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabljati občutljive podatke iz klasične denarnice z novim "
"zaledjem, sledite tem korakom:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a new GPG based wallet"
msgstr "Ustvarite novo denarnico, ki temelji na GPG"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launch &kwalletmanager5; using &krunner; (<keycombo>&Alt; <keycap>F2</"
"keycap></keycombo>) or other application launcher (menu) and select your old "
"wallet. Then choose <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export "
"as encrypted</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to create an archive file with your "
"sensitive data."
msgstr ""
"Zaženi &kwalletmanager5; z uporabo &krunner; (<keycombo>&Alt; <keycap>F2</"
"keycap></keycombo>) ali drug zaganjalnik aplikacij (meni) in izberite svojo "
"staro denarnico. Nato izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izvozi kot šifrirano</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da ustvarite "
"arhivsko datoteko z občutljivimi podatki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the new GPG based wallet then choose <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import encrypted</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and select "
"the file you just saved."
msgstr ""
"Izberite novo denarnico, ki temelji na GPG, nato izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uvozi šifrirano</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in izberite datoteko, ki ste jo pravkar shranili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to &systemsettings; <menuchoice><guimenu>Account Details</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>KDE Wallet</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and select the newly "
"created GPG based wallet from the <guilabel>Select wallet to use as default</"
"guilabel> combobox."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na &systemsettings; <menuchoice><guimenu>Podrobnosti o računu</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Denarnica KDE</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in izberite "
"novo ustvarjeno denarnico, ki temelji na GPG, v spustnem polju "
"<guilabel>Izberi denarnico za uporabo kot privzeto</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively use <guimenuitem>Import a wallet</guimenuitem> but in that "
"case you have to select the <filename class=\"extension\">.kwl</filename> "
"file corresponding to your old wallet, located in the folder <filename class="
"\"directory\">kwalletd</filename> in <userinput>qtpaths --paths "
"GenericDataLocation</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Druga možnost je, da uporabite <guimenuitem>Uvozi denarnico</guimenuitem>, "
"vendar morate v tem primeru izbrati datoteko <filename class=\"extension\">."
"kwl</filename>, ki ustreza vaši stari denarnici in se nahaja v mapi "
"<filename class=\"directory\">kwalletd</filename> v <userinput>qtpaths --"
"paths GenericDataLocation</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; supports multiple wallets, so for the most secure operation, you "
"should use one wallet for local passwords, and another for network passwords "
"and form data. You can configure this behavior in the &kwallet5; "
"&systemsettings; module, however the default setting is to store everything "
"in one wallet named <guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"&kwallet5; podpira več denarnic, zato za najbolj varno delovanje uporabite "
"eno denarnico za lokalna gesla in drugo za omrežna gesla in podatke "
"obrazcev. To vedenje lahko nastavite v oknu &kwallet5; &systemsettings; "
"vendar je privzeta nastavitev shranjevanje vsega v eno denarnico z imenom "
"<guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A wallet is by default closed, which means that you must supply a password "
"to open it. Once the wallet is opened, the contents can be read by any user "
"process, so this may be a security issue."
msgstr ""
"Denarnica je privzeto zaprta, kar pomeni, da morate vnesti geslo, da jo "
"odprete. Ko je denarnica odprta, lahko vsebino prebere kateri koli "
"uporabniški proces, zato je to lahko varnostna težava."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kwallet5;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kwallet5;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you visit &eg; the &kde; bugtracker and enter the login data for the "
"first time, a dialog pops up offering to store the password in an encrypted "
"wallet:"
msgstr ""
"Če obiščete &eg; &kde; bugtracker in prvič vnesete podatke za prijavo, se "
"prikaže pogovorno okno, ki ponuja shranjevanje gesla v šifrirano denarnico:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Request to save login information</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zahteva za shranjevanje podatkov za prijavo</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Request to save login information</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zahteva za shranjevanje podatkov za prijavo</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to store this information, select <guibutton>Store</guibutton> "
"to proceed. In case you did not create a wallet so far, the next dialog asks "
"for the encryption backend and creates a wallet named kdewallet."
msgstr ""
"Če želite te podatke shraniti, izberite <guibutton>Shrani</guibutton> za "
"nadaljevanje. Če denarnice še niste ustvarili, bo naslednje pogovorno okno "
"zahtevalo zaledje šifriranja in ustvarilo denarnico z imenom kdewallet."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next time you visit the same website again, the application retrieves the "
"login data from an open wallet and prefills the forms with these secrets."
msgstr ""
"Naslednjič, ko ponovno obiščete isto spletno mesto, aplikacija pridobi "
"podatke za prijavo iz odprte denarnice in vnaprej izpolni obrazce s temi "
"skrivnostmi."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Prefilled login information</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Vnaprej izpolnjeni podatki za prijavo</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Prefilled login information</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Vnaprej izpolnjeni podatki za prijavo</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the wallet is closed the application requests to open the wallet. Enter "
"the wallet password and click the <guibutton>Open</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če je denarnica zaprta, aplikacija zahteva odpiranje denarnice. Vnesite "
"geslo denarnice in kliknite gumb <guibutton>Odpri</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Request to open a wallet</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zahteva za odpiranje denarnice</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Request to open a wallet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zahteva za odpiranje denarnice</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This connects the application to the wallet, enables it to read the login "
"data from the wallet and to restore the login information for this website. "
"Once an application is connected to the wallet, it can automatically restore "
"any login information stored in the wallet."
msgstr ""
"To poveže aplikacijo z denarnico, ji omogoči branje podatkov za prijavo iz "
"denarnice in obnovitev podatkov za prijavo za to spletno mesto. Ko je "
"aplikacija povezana z denarnico, lahko samodejno obnovi vse podatke za "
"prijavo, shranjene v denarnici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kwalletmanager5;"
msgstr "&kwalletmanager5;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwalletmanager5; serves a number of functions. Firstly it allows you to see "
"if any wallets are open, which wallets those are, and which applications are "
"using each wallet. You can disconnect an application's access to a wallet "
"from within the &kwalletmanager5;."
msgstr ""
"&kwalletmanager5; služi številnim funkcijam. Najprej vam omogoča, da vidite, "
"ali so odprte denarnice, katere denarnice so to in katere aplikacije "
"uporabljajo posamezno denarnico. Dostop aplikacije do denarnice lahko "
"prekinete znotraj &kwalletmanager5;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may also manage the wallets installed on the system, creating and "
"deleting wallets and manipulating their contents (changing keys, ...)."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako lahko upravljate z denarnicami, nameščenimi v sistemu, ustvarjate "
"in brišete denarnice ter manipulirate z njihovo vsebino (menjava "
"ključev, ...)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kwalletmanager5; application is launched with <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Applications</guimenu><guisubmenu>System</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Wallet Management Tool</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the "
"application launcher. Alternatively start &krunner; with shortcut <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> and enter "
"<command>kwalletmanager5</command>."
msgstr ""
"&kwalletmanager5; aplikacija se zažene z <menuchoice> <guimenu>Aplikacije</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Sistem</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Orodje za upravljanje "
"denarnice</guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz zaganjalnika aplikacij. Druga "
"možnost je, da zaženete &krunner; z bližnjico <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> in vnesite <command>kwalletmanager5</"
"command>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click once on the system tray wallet icon to display the &kwalletmanager5; "
"window."
msgstr ""
"Enkrat kliknite ikono denarnice v sistemski vrstici, da prikažete "
"&kwalletmanager5; okno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Main window with one wallet</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Glavno okno z eno denarnico</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Main window with one wallet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavno okno z eno denarnico</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Main window with one wallet</para>"
msgstr "<para>Glavno okno z eno denarnico</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Wallet Window"
msgstr "Okno denarnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have more than one wallet all available wallets are shown on the left."
msgstr ""
"Če imate več kot eno denarnico, so vse razpoložljive denarnice prikazane na "
"levi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on a wallet in the &kwalletmanager5; window will display that "
"wallet's status and the contents of an opened wallet. A wallet may contain "
"any number of folders, which allow storing of password information. By "
"default a wallet will contain folders named Form Data and Passwords."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na denarnico v &kwalletmanager5; okno bo prikazalo stanje te "
"denarnice in vsebino odprte denarnice. Denarnica lahko vsebuje poljubno "
"število map, ki omogočajo shranjevanje podatkov o geslu. Denarnica bo "
"privzeto vsebovala mape z imenom Podatki obrazcev in Gesla."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Main window with two wallets</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Glavno okno z dvema denarnicama</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Main window with two wallets</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavno okno z dvema denarnicama</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Main window with two wallets</para>"
msgstr "<para>Glavno okno z dvema denarnicama</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guibutton>Open</guibutton> to display the content of a closed wallet. "
"You will be requested to enter the master password."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz vsebine zaprte denarnice uporabite <guibutton>Odpri</guibutton>. "
"Vnesti boste morali glavno geslo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contents tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Vsebina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>Contents</guilabel> tab has three sections:"
msgstr "Zavihek <guilabel>Vsebina</guilabel> ima tri razdelke:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid "A search line to filter the items of the current wallet"
msgstr "Iskalna vrstica za filtriranje elementov trenutne denarnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tree view of the folders contained in the wallet. Click the <guiicon>&gt;"
"</guiicon> / <guiicon>v</guiicon> icons to expand or collapse the tree view."
msgstr ""
"Drevesni pogled map v denarnici. Kliknite ikoni <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> / "
"<guiicon>v</guiicon>, da razširite ali strnete drevesni pogled."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contents of the selected folder entry at the right side. By default the "
"password and value are hidden. To display and edit them enable "
"<guilabel>Show values</guilabel> or click the <guilabel>Show Contents</"
"guilabel> button."
msgstr ""
"Vsebina vnosa izbrane mape na desni strani. Privzeto sta geslo in vrednost "
"skrita. Če jih želite prikazati in urediti, omogočite <guilabel>Pokaži "
"vrednosti</guilabel> ali kliknite gumb <guilabel>Pokaži vsebino</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Folders may be added or deleted via the context menu, and selecting a folder "
"will update the folder entry list and the summary display. Selecting a "
"folder entry will update the entry contents pane, and allow you to edit that "
"entry."
msgstr ""
"Mape lahko dodate ali izbrišete prek kontekstnega menija, z izbiro mape pa "
"se posodobita seznam vnosov map in prikaz povzetka. Če izberete vnos v mapo, "
"boste posodobili podokno z vsebino vnosa in omogočili urejanje tega vnosa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entries may also be created, renamed or deleted via the context menu for the "
"folder contents."
msgstr ""
"Vnose lahko tudi ustvarite, preimenujete ali izbrišete prek kontekstnega "
"menija za vsebino mape."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All folders and entries may be dragged and dropped into other wallets or "
"folders respectively. This allows a user to easily package up a new wallet "
"for transfer to another environment. For instance, a new wallet could be "
"created and copied onto a removable flash memory device. Important passwords "
"could be transferred there, so you have them available in other locations."
msgstr ""
"Vse mape in vnose lahko povlečete in spustite v druge denarnice ali mape. To "
"uporabniku omogoča enostavno pakiranje nove denarnice za prenos v drugo "
"okolje. Na primer, lahko ustvarite novo denarnico in jo kopirate na "
"izmenljivo bliskovno pomnilniško napravo. Tja se lahko prenesejo pomembna "
"gesla, zato jih imate na voljo na drugih lokacijah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import and Export"
msgstr "Uvoz in izvoz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to transfer your secrets to another device or computer use the "
"actions in the <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. With <guimenuitem>Export as "
"encrypted</guimenuitem> wallets can be exported into an encrypted archive "
"file. Importing this archive file with <guimenuitem>Import encrypted</"
"guimenuitem> you have to provide the master password of the wallet."
msgstr ""
"Če želite svoje skrivnosti prenesti v drugo napravo ali računalnik, "
"uporabite dejanja v meniju <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu>. Z "
"<guimenuitem>Izvozi kot šifrirano</guimenuitem> lahko denarnice izvozite v "
"šifrirano arhivsko datoteko. Pri uvozu te arhivske datoteke z "
"<guimenuitem>Uvozi šifrirano</guimenuitem> morate zagotoviti glavno geslo "
"denarnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively a <filename class=\"extension\">.xml</filename> file can be "
"used for transferring a wallet. Keep in mind that all secrets are stored as "
"plain text in this file."
msgstr ""
"Druga možnost je, da za prenos denarnice uporabite datoteko <filename class="
"\"extension\">.xml</filename>. Ne pozabite, da so vse skrivnosti v tej "
"datoteki shranjene kot golo besedilo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Entries Manually"
msgstr "Ročno dodajanje vnosov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the context menu with the &RMB; click on <guilabel>Maps</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Passwords</guilabel> in the <guilabel>Folder</guilabel> tree view. "
"Select <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>New Folder</"
"guimenuitem> and choose a name for the new entry."
msgstr ""
"Odprite kontekstni meni z &RMB; kliknite <guilabel>Zemljevidi</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Gesla</guilabel> v drevesnem pogledu <guilabel>Mape</guilabel>. "
"Izberite <guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Nova mapa</"
"guimenuitem> in izberite ime za nov vnos."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the folder contents pane select <guilabel>New Folder</guilabel> from the "
"context menu of <quote>Form Data</quote> or <quote>Passwords</quote>. For "
"passwords click the <guilabel>Show Contents</guilabel> button, enter the new "
"password. For Maps you have to add a <guilabel>Key</guilabel> and a "
"<guilabel>Value</guilabel>. Click the <guilabel>Save</guilabel> button to "
"store the new entries in the encrypted wallet file."
msgstr ""
"V podoknu z vsebino mape izberite <guilabel>Nova mapa</guilabel> v priročnem "
"meniju <quote>Podatki obrazca</quote> ali <quote>Gesla</quote>. Za gesla "
"kliknite gumb <guilabel>Pokaži vsebino</guilabel>, vnesite novo geslo. Za "
"Zemljevide morate dodati <guilabel>Ključ</guilabel> in <guilabel>Vrednost</"
"guilabel>. Kliknite gumb <guilabel>Shrani</guilabel>, da shranite nove vnose "
"v datoteko šifrirane denarnice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Applications tab</title>"
msgstr "<title>Zavihek Aplikacije</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Applications tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zavihek Aplikacije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Applications tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zavihek Aplikacije</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Applications tab</para>"
msgstr "<para>Zavihek Aplikacije</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first list shows all applications currently connected to the selected "
"wallet. Use the button at the right side of each entry to disconnect the "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Prvi seznam prikazuje vse aplikacije, ki so trenutno povezane z izbrano "
"denarnico. Za prekinitev povezave z aplikacijo uporabite gumb na desni "
"strani vsakega vnosa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the second list all applications are displayed which are authorized to "
"access the wallet. Use the button right of each entry in the list to revoke "
"the access."
msgstr ""
"Na drugem seznamu so prikazane vse aplikacije, ki so pooblaščene za dostop "
"do denarnice. Za preklic dostopa uporabite gumb desno od vsakega vnosa na "
"seznamu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kwallet5;"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &kwallet5;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wallet Preferences"
msgstr "Nastavitve denarnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; contains a small configuration panel with several options that "
"allow you to tune &kwallet5; to your personal preferences. The default "
"settings for &kwallet5; are sufficient for most users."
msgstr ""
"&kwallet5; vsebuje majhno konfiguracijsko ploščo z več možnostmi, ki vam "
"omogočajo nastavitev &kwallet5; glede na vaše osebne želje. Privzete "
"nastavitve za &kwallet5; zadostujejo za večino uporabnikov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the box to enable or disable the &kde; wallet subsystem entirely. If "
"this box is unchecked, then &kwallet5; is entirely disabled and none of the "
"other options here have any effect, nor will &kwallet5; record any "
"information, or offer to fill in forms for you."
msgstr ""
"Potrdite polje, da omogočite ali onemogočite &kde; podsistem denarnice v "
"celoti. Če to polje ni potrjeno, &kwallet5; je v celoti onemogočen in nobena "
"od drugih možnosti tukaj nima učinka, niti &kwallet5; beležijo kakršne koli "
"podatke ali ponudijo izpolnjevanje obrazcev namesto vas."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close Wallet"
msgstr "Zapri Denarnico"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close when unused for:"
msgstr "Zapri, ko se ne uporablja za:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Close the current wallet after a period of inactivity. If you check this "
"option, set the period in the box, default is 10 minutes. When a wallet is "
"closed, the password is needed to access it again."
msgstr ""
"Zaprite trenutno denarnico po obdobju nedejavnosti. Če izberete to možnost, "
"nastavite obdobje v polju, privzeto je 10 minut. Ko je denarnica zaprta, je "
"za ponoven dostop potrebno geslo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close when screensaver starts"
msgstr "Zapri, ko se zažene ohranjevalnik zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Close the wallet as soon as the screen saver starts. When a wallet is "
"closed, the password is needed to access it again."
msgstr ""
"Zaprite denarnico takoj, ko se zažene ohranjevalnik zaslona. Ko je denarnica "
"zaprta, je za ponoven dostop potrebno geslo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close when last application stops using it"
msgstr "Zapri, ko ga zadnja aplikacija preneha uporabljati"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Close the wallet as soon as applications that use it have stopped. Note that "
"your wallets will only be closed when all the applications that use it have "
"stopped. When a wallet is closed, the password is needed to access it again."
msgstr ""
"Zaprite denarnico takoj, ko se ustavijo aplikacije, ki jo uporabljajo. "
"Upoštevajte, da bodo vaše denarnice zaprte šele, ko se ustavijo vse "
"aplikacije, ki jih uporabljajo. Ko je denarnica zaprta, je za ponoven dostop "
"potrebno geslo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Wallet Selection"
msgstr "Samodejna izbira denarnice"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select wallet to use as default:"
msgstr "Izberite denarnico, ki jo želite uporabiti kot privzeto:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select which wallet you want to use as default wallet. Please keep in mind "
"that only the wallet named <guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel> will be opened "
"automatically at login, if this wallet and your login password are identical."
msgstr ""
"Izberite denarnico, ki jo želite uporabiti kot privzeto denarnico. "
"Upoštevajte, da se bo samo denarnica z imenom <guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel> "
"samodejno odprla ob prijavi, če sta ta denarnica in vaše geslo za prijavo "
"enaka."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "Different wallet for local passwords:"
msgstr "Druga denarnica za lokalna gesla:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "If checked, choose a different wallet for local passwords."
msgstr "Če je označeno, izberite drugo denarnico za lokalna gesla."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wallet Manager"
msgstr "Upravitelj denarnice"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show manager in system tray"
msgstr "Pokaži upravitelja v sistemski vrstici"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable the wallet manager to have its icon in the system tray."
msgstr "Omogoči upravitelju denarnice, da ima svojo ikono v sistemski vrstici."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide System tray icon when last wallet closes"
msgstr "Skrij ikono sistemske vrstice, ko se zapre zadnja denarnica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When there is no wallet in use anymore, remove the wallet icon from the "
"system tray."
msgstr ""
"Ko denarnica ni več v uporabi, odstranite ikono denarnice iz sistemske "
"vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, there is a button labeled <guibutton>Launch Wallet Manager</"
"guibutton>, which does precisely that."
msgstr ""
"Končno je na voljo gumb z oznako <guibutton>Zaženi upravitelja denarnice</"
"guibutton>, ki naredi natanko to."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "This button is only visible if &kwalletmanager5; is not running"
msgstr "Ta gumb je viden le, če &kwalletmanager5; ne teče"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Access Control</title>"
msgstr "<title>Nadzor dostopa</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "There is only one option on this page:"
msgstr "Na tej strani je samo ena možnost:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prompt when an application accesses a wallet"
msgstr "Poziv, ko aplikacija dostopa do denarnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "Signal you when an application gains access to a wallet."
msgstr "Opozori vas, ko aplikacija pridobi dostop do denarnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next there is a tree style view of the access controls for your wallets."
msgstr "Sledi drevesni pogled nadzora dostopa do vaših denarnic."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Access Control</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nadzor dostopa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Access Control</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nadzor dostopa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click with the &LMB; on the <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> symbol beside a wallet "
"name to expand the tree. You will see the name of each application that has "
"asked for access to the wallet, and the policy you set for it. You cannot "
"edit policies here, or add them, but it is possible to delete an entry by "
"&RMB; clicking on it and choosing <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem> from the "
"context menu that appears, or by simply selecting it and pressing the "
"<keysym>Del</keysym> key."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite z &LMB; na simbolu <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> poleg imena denarnice, "
"da razširite drevo. Videli boste ime vsake aplikacije, ki je zahtevala "
"dostop do denarnice, in pravilnik, ki ste ga nastavili zanjo. Tukaj ne "
"morete urejati pravilnikov ali jih dodajati, lahko pa izbrišete vnos z &RMB; "
"kliknite nanjo in izberite <guimenuitem>Izbriši</guimenuitem> v kontekstnem "
"meniju, ki se prikaže, ali pa jo preprosto izberite in pritisnite tipko "
"<keysym>Del</keysym>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An application that has been allowed access to a wallet is granted access to "
"all passwords stored inside."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija, ki ji je bil dovoljen dostop do denarnice, ima dostop do vseh "
"gesel, shranjenih v njej."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you erroneously configured an application not to use the &kwallet5; "
"delete the policy for this application here."
msgstr ""
"Če ste pomotoma konfigurirali aplikacijo, da ne uporablja &kwallet5; tukaj "
"izbrišite pravilnik za to aplikacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the next start of this application you can define a new policy for access "
"to the wallet."
msgstr ""
"Ob naslednjem zagonu te aplikacije lahko določite nov pravilnik za dostop do "
"denarnice."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Access request to open a wallet</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zahteva za dostop za odpiranje denarnice</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Access request to open a wallet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zahteva za dostop za odpiranje denarnice</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid "An application requesting access to a wallet"
msgstr "Aplikacija, ki zahteva dostop do denarnice"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Features"
msgstr "Napredne funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Wallets can be dragged from the &kwalletmanager5; window. This allows you to "
"drag the wallet to a file browser window, where you can choose to copy, "
"move, or link the wallet, as desired."
msgstr ""
"Denarnice lahko povlečete iz &kwalletmanager5; okno. To vam omogoča, da "
"povlečete denarnico v okno brskalnika datotek, kjer lahko po želji kopirate, "
"premaknete ali povežete denarnico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You might use this to save a wallet to portable media, such as a USB "
"keychain, so that you can take your passwords with you to work or on a "
"vacation, and still have easy access to important sites."
msgstr ""
"To lahko uporabite za shranjevanje denarnice na prenosni medij, kot je "
"obesek za ključe USB, tako da lahko vzamete svoja gesla s seboj v službo ali "
"na dopust in imate še vedno enostaven dostop do pomembnih mest."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credits and License"
msgstr "Zasluge in licenca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kwallet5; &copy; 2003 &George.Staikos;"
msgstr "&kwallet5; &copy; 2003 &George.Staikos;"

